Symbol.Script_3D:
toe_h = 0 front_cab = 0 rear_cab = 0 left_cab = 0 right_cab = 0 count_th = 0
if gs_detlevel_3D_m=0 then END if GLOB_CONTEXT>20 and GLOB_CONTEXT<40 then gs_detlevel_3D_m=1
if gs_detlevel_3D_m=1 then RESOL 4 if gs_detlevel_3D_m=2 then RESOL gs_resol
if not(gs_shadow) then SHADOW OFF
! --- END PANELS OPTION --- if dob_face then rear_cab = rear_cab if rear_panel then rear_cab = rear_cab + 0.02 if left_panel then left_cab = left_cab +0.02 if right_panel then right_cab = right_cab +0.02
addz placementHeight
unID=1
hotspot 0,0,0, unID : unID=unID+1 hotspot a,0,0, unID : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0,b,0, unID : unID=unID+1 hotspot a,b,0, unID : unID=unID+1
hotspot a, b, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot a, b, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot a, b, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot 0, b, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, b, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, b, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot a, 0, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot a, 0, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot a, 0, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2 : unID=unID+1
hotspot 0, 0, 0, unID, zzyzx, 1+128 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, -1, unID, zzyzx, 3 : unID=unID+1 hotspot 0, 0, zzyzx, unID, zzyzx, 2 : unID=unID+1
if gs_door_bw=0 then if gs_full_edit=1 then !! Door Panel Streching if gs_door_type_m > 0 then hotspot 0,front_cab,toe_h+door_h,unID,door_w,1+128 hotspot -1,front_cab,toe_h+door_h,unID,door_w,3 hotspot door_w,front_cab,toe_h+door_h,unID,door_w,2 endif endif endif
PEN gs_cont_pen MATERIAL gs_cabinet_mat
if gs_detlevel_3D_m=1 then addy fr_th1 mulID = 0 if right_panel and left_panel then addx 0.02 : mulID = mulID + 1 endif if not(right_panel) and left_panel then addx 0.02 : mulID = mulID + 1 endif
PRISM_ 5,zzyzx, 0, 0, 15, a - (left_panel* 0.02) - (right_panel * 0.02), 0, 15, a - (left_panel* 0.02) - (right_panel * 0.02), b - fr_th1 - (dob_face * fr_th1), 15, 0, b - fr_th1 - (dob_face * fr_th1), 15, 0, 0, -1 del 1 if mulID > 0 then del mulID endif endif
! CALL GENERAL BASE CABINET if gs_detlevel_3D_m=2 then
CALL "fa_gen_basecabinet" PARAMETERS a=a, b=b, zzyzx=zzyzx, gs_detlevel_3D_m=gs_detlevel_3D_m, dob_face=dob_face, count_th=count_th, front_cab=0, rear_cab=rear_cab, left_cab=left_cab,fr_th1=fr_th1, right_cab=right_cab, toe_h=toe_h, side_vis_m=0, sink=0, shelf_num=shelf_num, gs_ShelfMat=gs_ShelfMat, gs_cont_pen=gs_cont_pen, gs_shadow=gs_shadow, toe_mat=0, gs_cabinet_mat=gs_cabinet_mat, drawer=0, ToeHtps3D=0, basecab_unID=unID, returned_parameters unID endif
! --- CALL DOOR PANEL ----------------------------------------------------------
for ii=1 to (dob_face)+1 !*** double face
ADD left_cab,front_cab+fr_th1,toe_h !*** FRONT DOORS if gs_door_type_m > 0 then GOSUB 20 !*** FRONT LEFT DOOR ADDx a-left_cab-right_cab mulx -1 if gs_door_type_m > 0 then GOSUB 30 !*** FRONT RIGHT DOOR del 1 del 2
ADDY front_cab ROTZ 180 MULX -1 ADD 0,-B+rear_cab,0 next ii del (dob_face+1)*4
! --- CALL END PANELS ----------------------------------------------------------
if rear_panel=1 and dob_face=0 then if gs_door_bw=1 then door_w=(a-left_cab-right_cab)/3: door_h=ZZYZX-toe_h-count_th ADD door_w+left_cab,b-rear_cab,toe_h ROTZ 180 GOSUB 40 ADDX -door_w GOSUB 40 ADDX -door_w GOSUB 40 del 4 endif
if gs_door_bw=0 then door_w=door_w: door_h=ZZYZX-toe_h-count_th ADD door_w+left_cab,b-rear_cab,toe_h ROTZ 180 GOSUB 40 door_w=(a-door_w-left_cab-right_cab)/2 ADDX -door_w GOSUB 40 ADDX -door_w GOSUB 40 del 4 endif endif
if left_panel=1 then door_w=b-fr_th1-rear_cab-(fr_th1*dob_face): door_h=ZZYZX-toe_h-count_th !*** LEFT END PANEL ADD left_cab,door_w+fr_th1,toe_h ROTZ -90 GOSUB 40 del 2 endif
if right_panel=1 then door_w=b-fr_th1-rear_cab-(fr_th1*dob_face): door_h=ZZYZX-toe_h-count_th ADD a-right_cab,fr_th1,toe_h ROTZ 90 GOSUB 40 del 2 endif
del 1
END
! FRONT DOOR_LEFT 20: if gs_door_bw=1 then door_w1=(a-left_cab-right_cab)/3 else door_w1=(door_w-left_cab) endif
cabdoortyp_unID=unID CALL "fa_cabdoortyp" PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m=gs_detlevel_3D_m, gs_full_edit=gs_full_edit,door_ang=door_ang,door_w=door_w1,door_h=door_h, gs_door_type_m=gs_door_type_m,gs_cust_p=gs_cust_p,doorframe_w=doorframe_w, vert_gnum=vert_gnum,hor_gnum=hor_gnum,gs_cont_pen=gs_cont_pen, gs_shadow=gs_shadow,doorglas_mat=doorglas_mat,doorframe_mat=doorframe_mat, fr_th1=fr_th1,gs_bevel=gs_bevel, gs_knob_type_m=gs_knob_type_m,gs_knob_p_m=gs_knob_p_m,knob_size=knob_size, knob_pl_x=knob_pl_x,knob_pl_y=knob_pl_y, gs_knob_mat=gs_knob_mat, cabdoortyp_unID=cabdoortyp_unID, gs_cust_knob = gs_cust_knob, gs_customHandleLength = gs_customHandleLength, gs_customHandleHeight = gs_customHandleHeight, gs_customHandleDepth = gs_customHandleDepth, returned_parameters cabdoortyp_unID
unID = cabdoortyp_unID
return
! FRONT DOOR_RIGHT 30: if gs_door_bw=1 then door_w2=(a-left_cab-right_cab)/3 else door_w2=(a-door_w1-left_cab-right_cab)/2 endif
cabdoortyp_unID=unID CALL "fa_cabdoortyp" PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m=gs_detlevel_3D_m, gs_full_edit=gs_full_edit,door_ang=door_ang,door_w=door_w2,door_h=door_h, gs_door_type_m=gs_door_type_m,gs_cust_p=gs_cust_p,doorframe_w=doorframe_w, vert_gnum=vert_gnum,hor_gnum=hor_gnum,gs_cont_pen=gs_cont_pen, gs_shadow=gs_shadow,doorglas_mat=doorglas_mat,doorframe_mat=doorframe_mat, fr_th1=fr_th1,gs_bevel=gs_bevel, gs_knob_type_m=gs_knob_type_m,gs_knob_p_m=gs_knob_p_m,knob_size=knob_size, knob_pl_x=knob_pl_x,knob_pl_y=knob_pl_y, gs_knob_mat=gs_knob_mat, cabdoortyp_unID=cabdoortyp_unID, gs_cust_knob = gs_cust_knob, gs_customHandleLength = gs_customHandleLength, gs_customHandleHeight = gs_customHandleHeight, gs_customHandleDepth = gs_customHandleDepth, returned_parameters cabdoortyp_unID
unID = cabdoortyp_unID
ADDx door_w2*2 mulx -1
cabdoortyp_unID=unID CALL "fa_cabdoortyp" PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m=gs_detlevel_3D_m, gs_full_edit=gs_full_edit,door_ang=door_ang,door_w=door_w2,door_h=door_h, gs_door_type_m=gs_door_type_m,gs_cust_p=gs_cust_p,doorframe_w=doorframe_w, vert_gnum=vert_gnum,hor_gnum=hor_gnum,gs_cont_pen=gs_cont_pen, gs_shadow=gs_shadow,doorglas_mat=doorglas_mat,doorframe_mat=doorframe_mat, fr_th1=fr_th1,gs_bevel=gs_bevel, gs_knob_type_m=gs_knob_type_m,gs_knob_p_m=gs_knob_p_m,knob_size=knob_size, knob_pl_x=knob_pl_x,knob_pl_y=knob_pl_y, gs_knob_mat=gs_knob_mat, cabdoortyp_unID=cabdoortyp_unID, gs_cust_knob = gs_cust_knob, gs_customHandleLength = gs_customHandleLength, gs_customHandleHeight = gs_customHandleHeight, gs_customHandleDepth = gs_customHandleDepth, returned_parameters cabdoortyp_unID
unID = cabdoortyp_unID
del 2 return
! END PANELS 40: ! on rear panel there is no glas and grilles and knobs!! door_ang=0 gs_knob_type_m=0 If iEndPanelType = 1 then gs_door_type_m=1 If iEndPanelType = 2 then gs_door_type_m=2 If iEndPanelType = 4 then gs_door_type_m=11 If iEndPanelType = 7 then gs_door_type_m=4 If iEndPanelType = 9 then gs_door_type_m=6 If iEndPanelType = 99 then gs_door_type_m=10 gs_full_edit=0
cabdoortyp_unID=unID CALL "fa_cabdoortyp" PARAMETERS ALL cabdoortyp_unID=cabdoortyp_unID, fr_th1=0.02,gs_cust_p=gs_cust_p_end,doorframe_w=doorframe_w_end, doorframe_mat=doorframe_mat_end,doorglas_mat=doorframe_mat_end, gs_bevel=gs_bevel, returned_parameters cabdoortyp_unID
unID = cabdoortyp_unID
return
